    "body": "I'm sure some CSS expert can tell me what I'm doing wrong but the workaround I used was to change `<div class=\"browser\">` to `<div class=\"hack-browser\">` and then add the following script at the bottom\n\n```\n<script>\ndocument.querySelector(\".hack-browser\").className = \"browser\";\n</script>\n```\n"
